ure" "254807"\n<img src=rdb://256071>\n\na HQ Floorplan\n( ie : #L "Floorplan - Neutral Small Organization Headquarters" "254790" )\n<img src=rdb://121435>\n\n#L "Fertilized Giant Chirop Egg" "247788"\n<img src=rdb://20405>\n\n#L "Unrefined Notum Salt" "247786"\n<img src=rdb://247785>\n\n#L "Slow-Killing Poison" "247791"\n<img src=rdb://100335>\n\n#L "Uncle Bazzit''s Bio-Mechanical AI" "247794"\n<img src=rdb://247793>\n\n#L "Advanced Bio-Comminutor" "154332"\n<img src=rdb://149951>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe #C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nUnrefined Notum Salt\n#C15+#C20\nFertilized Giant Chirop Egg\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://20405>\n#L "Mutating Giant Chirop Egg" "247789"\n#C16Skills: |  ??  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nSlow-Killing Poison\n#C15+#C20\nMutating Giant Chirop Egg\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://20405>\n#L "Poisoned Giant Chirop Egg" "247790"\n#C16Skills: |  ??  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nBio-Comminutor\n#C15+#C20\nPoisoned Giant Chirop Egg\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://99239>\n#L "Mutating Bio-Pulp" "247792"\n#C16Skills: |  ??  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nMutating Bio-Pulp\n#C15+#C20\nUncle Bazzit''s Bio-Mechanical AI\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://247793>\n#L "Bio-Mechanical Computer" "247795"\n#C16Skills: |  ??  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nBio-Mechanical Computer\n#C15+#C20\nRegular Building Structure\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://256070>\n#L "Superior Building Structure" "254829"\n#C16Skills: |  ??  |#C20\n\n#C14------------------------------#C20\n\nHQ Floorplan\n#C15+#C20\nSuperior Building Structure\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://255790>\na HQ Stucture\n( ie : #L "Small Omni-Tek Organization Headquarters" "254210" )\n#C16Skills: |  ??  |#C20\n\n\n<highlight>4) Build High QL HQ Structure<end>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients #C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Kyr''Ozch Viral Serum" "254805"\n<img sr