INSERT INTO recipes (id, name, author, recipe) VALUES (112, 'Solar-Powered Engineer Pistol', '', '<highlight>Step 1: Solar-Powered Pistol<end>\n\nJump to step 2 if you kept the Start Up Pistol you''ve been given when you created your Engineer.\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Basic Calculator" "156058"\n<img src=rdb://156319>\n\n#L "Auto Targeting Computer -IIR 4 -Ultra-" "137291"\n<img src=rdb://130761>\n\n#L "Jandawit Cleanup Cluster" "137281"\n<img src=rdb://130755>\n\n#L "Irreparable River MV" "123667"\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nAuto Targeting Computer -IIR 4 -Ultra-\n#C15+#C20\nBasic Calculator\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://130762>\n#L "Solar-Powered Weapon Supervisor" "164523"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nJandawit Cleanup Cluster\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Weapon Supervisor\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://130758>\n#L "Solar-Powered Weapon Device" "164525"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nSolar-Powered Weapon Device\n#C15+#C20\nIrreparable River MV\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Pistol" "121567"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 2: Solar-Powered Tinker Pistol<end>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Jensen Personal Ore Extractor" "150281"\n<img src=rdb://149947>\n\n#L "Screwdriver" "150922"\n<img src=rdb://151011>\n\n#L "Robotic Self-Preservation System" "164529"\n<img src=rdb://11606>\n\n#L "Notum Chip" "136623"\n<img src=rdb://25794>\n#C15or#C20\n#L "Notum Fragment" "136625"\n<img src=rdb://25795>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nScrewdriver\n#C15+#C20\nJensen Personal Ore Extractor\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://149948>\n#L "Modified Jensen Ore Extractor" "164527"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nRobotic Self-Preservation System\n#C15+#C20\nModified Jensen Ore Extractor\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://149948>\n#L "Unstable Preservation System" "164531"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nNotum\n#C15+#C20\nUnstable Preservation System\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://149947>\n#L "Stable Preservation System" "164536"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nStable Preservation System\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Tinker Pistol" "164490"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 3: Solar-Powered Mender Pistol<end>\n\nIncrease the QL of your pistol to 39 by right-clicking on it.\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nMechanical Analyzer (#L "recipe" "/tell <myname> rshow 67")\n<img src=rdb://156512>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nMechanical Analyzer\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Tinker Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Mender Pistol" "164498"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 4: Solar-Powered Mechanic Pistol<end>\n\nIncrease the QL of your pistol to 99 by right-clicking on it.\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Electrical Engineering Tutoring Device" "55693"\n<img src=rdb://99294>\n\n#L "Hacker Tool" "87814"\n<img src=rdb://99282>\n\n#L "Disposal Unit Electrical Toolset" "164552"\n<img src=rdb://12710>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nHacker Tool\n#C15+#C20\nElectrical Engineering Tutoring Device\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://161873>\n#L "Hacked Electrical Engineering Tutoring Device" "164550"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nHacked Electrical Engineering Tutoring Device\n#C15+#C20\nDisposal Unit Electrical Toolset\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://161873>\n#L "Modified Electrical Toolset" "164553"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nModified Electrical Toolset\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Mender Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Mechanic Pistol" "164501"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 5: Solar-Powered Machinist Pistol<end>\n\nIncrease the QL of your pistol to 139 by right-clicking on it.\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nNotum Threaded Backpack\n(#L "recipe" "/tell <myname> rshow 78")\n<img src=rdb://99660>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nNotum Threaded Backpack\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Mechanic Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Machinist Pistol" "164511"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 6: Solar-Powered Engineer Pistol<end>\n\nIncrease the QL of your pistol to 179 by right-clicking on it.\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Experimental Nanobot Classifying Computer" "164568"\n<img src=rdb://72783>\n\n#L "Mist-Filled Jar" "164566"\n<img src=rdb://154194>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nExperimental Nanobot Classifying Computer\n#C15+#C20\nMist-Filled Jar\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://72783>\n#L "Energized Nanobot Transmitter" "164574"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nEnergized Nanobot Transmitter\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Machinist Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Engineer Pistol" "164513"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 7: Solar-Powered Master Engineer Pistol<end>\n\nIncrease the QL of your pistol to 199 by right-clicking on it.\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Accelerated NCU" "164608" ( #L "recipe" "/tell <myname> rshow 1" )\n<img src=rdb://13367>\n\n#L "Crystalized Medusa Queen Hippocampus" "164598"\n<img src=rdb://156559>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nAccelerated NCU\n#C15+#C20\nCrystalized MedusaQueen Hippocampus\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://100323>\n#L "Symbiotic NCU" "164620"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nSymbiotic NCU\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Engineer Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://29116>\n#L "Solar-Powered Master Engineer Pistol" "164515"\n#C16Skills: |  WS  |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 8: Infused Solar-Powered Master Engineer Pistol<end>\n\nYou must have Lost Eden Expansion to use the pistol once modified beyond this point!\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Dust Brigade Solar Notum Infuser" "274558"\n<img src=rdb://218768>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nDust Brigade Solar Notum Infuser\n#C15+#C20\nSolar-Powered Master Engineer Pistol\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://264789>\n#L "Infused Solar-Powered Master Engineer Pistol" "274557"\n#C16Skills: | 1000WS,1800ME,1800EE |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n\n<highlight>Step 9: Augmented Master Engineer Pistol<end>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Ingredients#C20\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\n#L "Crude Upgrade Kit" "274975"\n<img src=rdb://218768>\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Recipe#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nInfused Solar-Powered Master Engineer Pistol\n#C15+#C20\nCrude Upgrade Kit\n#C15=#C20\n<img src=rdb://264789>\n#L "Augmented Master Engineer Pistol" "274973"\n#C16Skills: | 1500WS,2100ME,2100EE |#C20\n\n#C16------------------------------\n#C12Comments#C16\n#C16------------------------------#C20\n\nThe engineers best friend (besides his pet robots and his screwdriver - and <myname> ofc) ... now has an extra 2 steps of upgrading for those high level engis with Lost Eden Expansions.\n');
